sentences: Rosario del Carmen González Flores better known as Rosario Flores (Spanish pronunciation: [roˈsaɾjo floɾes]; born 4 November 1963) is a two-time Latin Grammy Award-winning Spanish singer.
Her second son, Pedro Antonio, was born on 21 January 2006, the same day as his grandmother Lola Flores.
